  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Keywords: Ninjutsu, Bukijutsu</p>\n<p>You throw a single weapon, when you do, you quickly multiply it five-fold, creating multiple copies of it while in transit. Creatures within this jutsu's range must succeed a Dexterity saving throw taking 5dX + your Dexterity modifier on a failed save, or half as much on a success. (X equals the original Damage die of the thrown weapon d4, d6, d8, d10, d12).</p>\n<p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2dX.</p>",
